      "content": "i dont even know why im still staring at this screen. everything is just... gone. the funding got pulled, my last three months of data are useless, and i feel like there's nothing left of me. i've spent my whole life building this one thing and now it's just a void. i'm just so incredibly tired of trying to fix things that are fundamentally broken. i just want the noise to stop.",
